According to police, the relationship had been developing for more than a year and turned physical early last month as it was ‘too late’ to stop it, Bates had told the relative. 

‘This particular student and her had become quite close over about the last year, or so,’ said Lt. Mark Wiegert of the Calumet County Sheriff's Department told Fox 11. 

