Lt. Wiegert added that there is no reason to believe there are other victims.

Bates, of Hilbert, has appeared in court today charged with four felony counts of sexual assault of a student by school staff.

The married mother-of-three was arrested on Monday after the relationship came to light, and resigned from her job at Appleton West High School, Appleton.

